15. PROOF OF AUTHORSHIP

The Founder's sole authorship is established by:

   a. BIOMETRIC IDENTITY: Fingerprint (Touch ID), iris (Optic ID), and
      facial recognition (Face ID) registered on the originating device.

   b. ORIGINAL ARTIFACTS: The originating development device, source
      repositories, backup archives, configuration files, workspace
      documents, the L7 inception record, and the complete chain of
      custody from inception to present.

   c. GIT COMMIT HISTORY: The complete, unbroken commit history at
      github.com/avalia1/L7_WAY demonstrating iterative development
      from first concept through present — each commit timestamped
      and authored by the Founder.

   d. SEALED ARCHIVES: SHA-256 checksummed documents in the salt domain,
      timestamped at moment of creation, independently verifiable.
